==制作==
该片的艺术手法是“[[无厘头|无厘头]]”。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://ent.newssc.org/system/2014/01/21/013905559.shtml|title= 《大话天仙》剧情简介|accessdate= 2014-04-11|date= 2014-01-21|work= 四川新闻网|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140209035129/http://ent.newssc.org/system/2014/01/21/013905559.shtml|archive-date= 2014-02-09|dead-url= yes}}</ref>

林雪出演一个外貌丑但是内心善良的角色，好比是《[[巴黎圣母院|巴黎圣母院]]》里的著名丑人卡西莫多。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2014-01/08/c_125972037.htm |title=《大话天仙》最丑角色 林雪演绎中国版卡西莫多 |accessdate=2014-04-11 |date=2014-01-08 |work=新华网 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502150254/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2014-01/08/c_125972037.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《大话天仙》由香港导演刘镇伟执导，郑中基、孙俪分别担纲男女主角。有传言称，该片后半部分不是由原班人马拍摄，是烂尾电影，此说法获得导演刘镇伟在他个人微博上证实<ref>{{cite web |url=http://weibo.com/1691954411/AeyIi0KN2 |language= |title=劉鎮偉2013年10月18日微博 |publisher=劉鎮偉新浪微博 |date=2013-10-18 |accessdate=2014-05-07 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408051931/http://weibo.com/1691954411/AeyIi0KN2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/w/2014-01-09/23534078243.shtml |title=《大话天仙》将映 导演演员均撇清关系 |date=2014-01-09 |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2014-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109181511/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/w/2014-01-09/23534078243.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是电影方“华录百纳”回应称，该片制作良好<ref>{{cite web |url=http://business.sohu.com/20131101/n389415383.shtml |language= |title=[互动]华录百纳:《大话天仙》上映时间未定(图) |publisher=搜狐 |date=2013-11-01 |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929175437/http://business.sohu.com/20131101/n389415383.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

